description: Next level brownie This super easy dessert looks super impressive for how simple it is. Filled with cookies & cream vegan ice-cream and fresh raspberries, bring these brownie slices to your next summer party.
name: Brownie And Raspberry IceCream Sandwich Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 L plantitude frozen dessert cookies & cream

recipeInstructions.text: Spoon frozen dessert over one brownie and smooth. Press in raspberries, then top with other brownie. Freeze for 4 hours, or overnight until frozen dessert is firm. Cut into squares and serve immediately.
